{
  "version": "2.11",
  "children": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "rzSpi",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 40,
      "name": "title",
      "fill": "#111111",
      "content": "开口｜词语联想训练｜清晰版低保真原型",
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 30,
      "fontWeight": "600"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "3NwHs",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 86,
      "name": "sub",
      "fill": "#444444",
      "content": "说明：这里不把 Pencil 当成真实动态原型工具，而是把动态规则翻译成完整状态稿，便于产品判断逻辑。",
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontWeight": "normal"
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "MmUs2",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 130,
      "name": "共享规则板",
      "width": 1340,
      "height": 300,
      "fill": "#FAFAFA",
      "cornerRadius": 20,
      "stroke": {
        "thickness": 2,
        "fill": "#111111"
      },
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 14,
      "padding": 24,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "W48KC",
          "fill": "#111111",
          "content": "共享产品规则",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 24,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "c90Ud",
          "fill": "#111111",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "1. 每轮固定 16 张卡 = 8 个名词 + 8 个形容词\n2. 用户在翻牌过程中自由选择 2 个词，选满后开始一次联想表达\n3. 当 16 张卡全部翻开时，本轮训练完成\n4. 免费用户最多 3 轮，第 4 轮开始触发会员拦截\n5. 下一轮必须换新词池，且与上一轮词语不重复",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 15,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "YIryp",
          "fill": "#444444",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Pencil 能做什么：明确页面状态、流程、信息结构。\nPencil 不能真实运行什么：随机发词、自动去重、真实翻牌、次数自动扣减。\n所以这次输出是“状态稿”，不是“运行时交互Demo”。",
          "lineHeight": 1.6,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "A5ySs",
      "x": 80,
      "y": 470,
      "name": "方案A 清晰版",
      "width": 3000,
      "height": 1100,
      "fill": "#FAFAFA",
      "cornerRadius": 24,
      "stroke": {
        "thickness": 2,
        "fill": "#111111"
      },
      "layout": "none",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "HR28u",
          "x": 40,
          "y": 28,
          "name": "aTitle",
          "fill": "#111111",
          "content": "方案A｜单页主界面 + 底部抽屉表达",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 24,
          "fontWeight": "600"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "5ZQVj",
          "x": 40,
          "y": 90,
          "name": "A-说明板",
          "width": 620,
          "height": 950,
          "fill": "#FFFFFF",
          "cornerRadius": 18,
          "stroke": {
            "thickness": 2,
            "fill": "#111111"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 16,
          "padding": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "OjZE4",
              "fill": "#111111",
              "content": "A版说明",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 22,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "zT3wa",
              "fill": "#111111",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "定位：首版最推荐。所有关键动作都在同一主界面里完成，只有底部抽屉状态在变化。",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "qhS8F",
              "fill": "#111111",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "本轮词池（完整展示，便于判断合理性）\n名词：河流 / 岛屿 / 灯塔 / 城市 / 森林 / 桥梁 / 邮差 / 火车\n形容词：勇敢 / 潮湿 / 明亮 / 迟缓 / 锋利 / 安静 / 拥挤 / 温热",
              "lineHeight": 1.65,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "z6Rgx",
              "fill": "#111111",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "状态顺序\n状态1：进入本轮，16张卡都在\n状态2：已翻若干张，并选中2词\n状态3：底部抽屉展开，开始一次联想表达\n状态4：本轮翻完，刷新下一轮不重复词池",
              "lineHeight": 1.65,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "d21L8",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "height": 260,
              "fill": "#FAFAFA",
              "cornerRadius": 16,
              "stroke": {
                "thickness": 2,
                "fill": "#111111"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "WBs24",
              "fill": "#111111",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "为什么这版最轻：用户不需要频繁切换页面，返回继续翻牌最顺，最适合小程序首版验证。",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
